<h2 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:22px;font-weight:600;color:{{defaultVal textColor "#38322d"}};">SMTP Configuration Test</h2>
<p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;color:{{defaultVal textColor "#38322d"}};line-height:1.6;">
  If you're reading this, your SMTP email configuration is working correctly.
</p>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
       style="margin:0 0 24px;background-color:{{defaultVal infoBoxBg "#e9e6dc"}};border-radius:8px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:16px 20px;">
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:{{defaultVal textColor "#38322d"}};font-weight:500;">
        &#10003;&ensp;Connection successful
      </p>
      <p style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:{{defaultVal textColor "#38322d"}};">
        Emails sent from {{appName}} will be delivered via <strong>{{host}}</strong> on port <strong>{{port}}</strong>.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:{{defaultVal textColor "#38322d"}};opacity:0.5;line-height:1.5;">
  This is an automated test email sent from the {{appName}} admin configuration panel. No action is required.
</p>
